entries.title: Bright, Shiny Lure
entries.split_quest_alert: Imperial High Command:<Now that the rebels have that data it is time to spring our plan. Stand by for further instructions.>
entries.shields_depleted: There went our shields. Prepare to get out of here.
entries.hull_half: Hull at half strength. Shouldn't be too much longer now.
entries.found_loc: Tactical Computer:<Destination located. Awaiting arrival of escort ship.>
entries.failed_protect: Nice work, pilot. The rebels should easily take control of the ship and find the information we planted on board.
entries.failed_destroy: Nice work, pilot. The rebels should scan the wreckage and find the false information we planted.
entries.complete: Pilot maybe you didn't understand that you were supposed to let the rebels take the ship. Report to your superior immediately.
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer:<Enemy fighter destroyed. Detecting no further ships.>
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer:<Enemy fighters detected. Incoming at high speeds.>
entries.arrived_at_loc: Wait for the decoy shuttle to arrive and then begin the mission.
entries.abort: What are you doing, pilot? You are aborting too early.
